      "span_text": "On the other hand, edible film using CMC 10%, 20% and 25% characteristics approach HDPE plastic when viewed from the aspect of tensile strength. The increasing and decreasing of the tensile strength depend on the strength of the material used in the filmmaking, to form large and strong molecular bonds."
